INSERT INTO posts VALUES('ed9d0692-e517-4c2c-b0f4-a375cd869ff6','e1a1fe52-a440-4286-a40d-2f1240aaa64a','46391572','Ask HN: What did you read in 2025?','I mostly read newspapers and technical journals, but two books that I read that made an impression: &quot;The Changing World Order&quot; and &quot;The Gulag Archipelago&quot;.','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46391572','news.ycombinator.com',NULL,'kwar13','https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id=kwar13',335,'{"en":{"title":"Ask HN: What did you read in 2025?","summary":"I mostly read newspapers and technical journals, but two books that I read that made an impression: &quot;The Changing World Order&quot; and &quot;The Gulag Archipelago&quot;."},"zh":{"title":"问HN：2025年你读了什么？","summary":"我主要阅读报纸和技术期刊，但我读过的两本书给人留下了深刻的印象：《不断变化的世界秩序》和《古拉格群岛》。"},"ja":{"title":"HN に尋ねる ： 2025 年に何を読みましたか ？","summary":"私は 主に 新聞 や 技術 雑誌 を読 みました が 、 印象 に残 った 本は  2   冊 あります 。&quot;変化 する 世界の 秩序&quot;そして&quot;グラ グ 諸 島&quot;."}}',1,1767348982,'["Ask HN"]',1766753716,1767348982,1767348982,'Ask HN: What did you read in 2025?','I mostly read newspapers and technical journals, but two books that I read that made an impression: &quot;The Changing World Order&quot; and &quot;The Gulag Archipelago&quot;.','en','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46391572');
INSERT INTO posts VALUES('7f8694ac-31cd-418e-a6f7-98e99450cdb7','e1a1fe52-a440-4286-a40d-2f1240aaa64a','46415911','Ask HN: Loneliness at 19, how to cope?','I am a college student and for my entire life I have been lonely. This is probably taken a very heavy toll on my mental health but that’s another story. I’ve never been able to make friends and keep meaningful connections that last a long time. In fact I’d go as far as saying I have never had a friend, and I currently don’t have any. My phone is empty, when I go to school nobody talks to me and when I do find people who seem to have some kind of interest in me, it usually doesn’t last very long ','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46415911','news.ycombinator.com',NULL,'yresting','https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id=yresting',61,'{"en":{"title":"Ask HN: Loneliness at 19, how to cope?","summary":"I am a college student and for my entire life I have been lonely. This is probably taken a very heavy toll on my mental health but that’s another story. I’ve never been able to make friends and keep meaningful connections that last a long time. In fact I’d go as far as saying I have never had a friend, and I currently don’t have any. My phone is empty, when I go to school nobody talks to me and when I do find people who seem to have some kind of interest in me, it usually doesn’t last very long "},"zh":{"title":"问HN：19岁孤独，如何应对？","summary":"我是一名大学生，一生都很孤独。这可能对我的心理健康造成了非常严重的影响，但那是另一回事了。我从未能够结交朋友并保持持续很长时间的有意义的联系。事实上，我甚至会说我从来没有朋友，而且我现在也没有。我的手机是空的，当我去学校时没有人和我说话，当我确实发现似乎对我有某种兴趣的人时，通常不会持续很长时间 "},"ja":{"title":"HN に尋ねる ： 19 歳の孤独、対処する方法 ？","summary":"私は大学生で、一生孤独でした。これはおそらく私のメンタルヘルスに非常に重い犠牲を払うが、それは別の話である。友達を作ることができず、長く続く意味のあるつながりを保つことができました。実際、私は決して友達がいなかったと言っても、現在もいない。私の電話は空で、学校に行くときは誰も私に話しかけず、私に何らかの関心を持っているように見える人々を見つけるとき、それは通常あまり長くは続かない。 "}}',1,1767348984,'["Ask HN"]',1766967220,1767348984,1767348984,'Ask HN: Loneliness at 19, how to cope?','I am a college student and for my entire life I have been lonely. This is probably taken a very heavy toll on my mental health but that’s another story. I’ve never been able to make friends and keep meaningful connections that last a long time. In fact I’d go as far as saying I have never had a friend, and I currently don’t have any. My phone is empty, when I go to school nobody talks to me and when I do find people who seem to have some kind of interest in me, it usually doesn’t last very long ','en','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46415911');
INSERT INTO posts VALUES('2748df4d-91af-4696-9694-ee1b2af18619','e1a1fe52-a440-4286-a40d-2f1240aaa64a','46434821','Ask HN: Any example of successful vibe-coded product?','Many people talk about vibe-coding and about the different ways to use this development &quot;methodology&quot; successfully. I wonder though if anyone really managed to push to production anything that has been fully or almost fully created through LLM assisted coding. Do you have anything to share, whether you or someone else created it? Possibly something more complex than a static webpage.','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46434821','news.ycombinator.com',NULL,'sirnicolaz','https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id=sirnicolaz',79,'{"en":{"title":"Ask HN: Any example of successful vibe-coded product?","summary":"Many people talk about vibe-coding and about the different ways to use this development &quot;methodology&quot; successfully. I wonder though if anyone really managed to push to production anything that has been fully or almost fully created through LLM assisted coding. Do you have anything to share, whether you or someone else created it? Possibly something more complex than a static webpage."},"zh":{"title":"询问HN：有任何成功的音频编码产品的例子吗？","summary":"许多人谈论振动编码以及成功使用这种开发方法的不同方法。我想知道是否有人真的设法将通过LLM辅助编码完全或几乎完全创建的任何东西推向生产。您有什么要分享的吗，无论是您还是其他人创建的？可能比静态网页更复杂。"},"ja":{"title":"HN に尋ねる ： 成功したバイブコード製品の例はありますか ？","summary":"多くの人がバイブコーディングやこの開発のさまざまな使い方について話します&quot;方法論&quot;成功しましたLLM アシストコーディングによって完全にまたはほぼ完全に作成されたものを実際にプロダクションにプッシュすることができた人はいますか ？あなたや誰かが作成したかどうか、共有したいものはありますか ？静的なウェブページよりも複雑なものかもしれません。"}}',1,1767348986,'["Ask HN"]',1767111503,1767348986,1767348986,'Ask HN: Any example of successful vibe-coded product?','Many people talk about vibe-coding and about the different ways to use this development &quot;methodology&quot; successfully. I wonder though if anyone really managed to push to production anything that has been fully or almost fully created through LLM assisted coding. Do you have anything to share, whether you or someone else created it? Possibly something more complex than a static webpage.','en','https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=46434821');
